overview: Fresh off the release of their 1st ever DVD titled MEN, See HIM Fuck is back at it with a new DVD titled MEN 2. Directed by Johnny Robins, the second installment in the “Focused On HIM” series features Brickzilla with Natalie Porkman,Criss Simon with Kyler Quinn, Louie Smalls with Blair Underwood, and Ridge Crix with Jenifer Jane.
title: Men 2
